Properties.commandText:
SELECT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Users" AS "u"
    WHERE NOT ("u"."IsDeleted"))

SELECT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "Products" AS "p"
    WHERE NOT ("p"."IsDeleted"))

SELECT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "ProductMachines" AS "p"
    WHERE NOT ("p"."IsDeleted"))

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Date", "c"."Eur", "c"."Gbp", "c"."Try", "c"."Usd"
FROM "Currency" AS "c"
WHERE rtrim(rtrim(strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%f', "c"."Date", 'start of day'), '0'), '.') = rtrim(rtrim(strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%f', 'now', 'start of day'), '0'), '.')
LIMIT 1

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Name", "c0"."Id", "c0"."Name"
FROM "Cities" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN "Counties" AS "c0" ON "c"."Id" = "c0"."CityId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Name", 0, "c0"."Id", "c0"."Name", "c1"."Id", "c1"."Name"
FROM "Counties" AS "c"
INNER JOIN "Cities" AS "c0" ON "c"."CityId" = "c0"."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Counties" AS "c1" ON "c0"."Id" = "c1"."CityId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "c0"."Id"
